<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.7.4">
<l>oḷiyā veṇṇe yuṇṭāṉeṉ ṟuralō ṭāycci yoṇkayiṟṟāl</l>
<l>viḷiyā vārkka vāppuṇṭu vimmi yaḻutāṉ meṉmalarmēl</l>
<l>kaḷiyā vaṇṭu kaḷḷuṇṇak kāmar teṉṟa lalartūṟṟa</l>
<l>naḷirvāy mullai muṟuvalikkum naṟaiyūr niṉṟa nampiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who wailed, sobbing, being stuck when tied</l>
<l rend="indent">with an excellent rope to a mortar,</l>
<l>By the herdess while angry that he ate up the ghee while hiding,</l>
<l>Is the noble who stands in Naṟaiyūr where cool lips of jasmine smile,</l>
<l>As the beautiful southern breeze scatters blossoms,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] as the bees sip nectar while frolicking on tender blossoms.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
